The Dangerous Lives of Altar Boys;;79;;77;;R;;Francis Doyle (Emile Hirsch) and Tim Sullivan (Kieran Culkin), and their closest friends, are fighting the stultifying repression of their parish school. Foremost among the forces of evil is the stern and disapproving nun, Sister Assumpta (Jodie Foster), who rules their lives. She seizes their artwork one day, setting the boys on an obsessed trail of revenge that ultimately changes their lives.;;Drama;;Peter Care;;2002;;Kieran Culkin,Jena Malone,Emile Hirsch,Vincent D'Onofrio,Jodie Foster,Jake Richardson,Tyler Long;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dangerous_lives_of_altar_boys